sequenceDiagram
  participant Edge as Edge Node
  participant GW as API Gateway
  participant Verify as Verify Service
  participant State as State Service
  participant Bus as Event Bus
  participant Graph as Trust Graph
  participant Ledger as Audit Ledger

  Edge->>GW: POST /v4/packets (signed raw body)
  GW->>Verify: forward + idempotency context
  Verify->>Verify: signature + replay checks
  Verify->>State: apply derived state (idempotent)
  Verify->>Ledger: append audit event (async OK)
  State->>Bus: state.updated
  Bus->>Graph: state.updated
  Graph->>Bus: graph.edges.inferred + clusters.snapshot
